snippet.title: Giana Sisters FANGAME DEMO Playthrough
snippet.description:
Download here:
https://mizunoketsuban.itch.io/giana-sisters-fangame-demo

A playthrough of the fangame I've been steadily working on, made in Pixel Game Maker MV.My mission statement was to create a game that celebrates every aspect of the series in one way or another, and to push a story between Giana and her oft-forgotten sister Maria.

I'm currently working on this project mostly solo, but if anyone is interested in helping me make this dream a reality, don't be afraid to contact me.
